sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant CLI as contextos CLI
  participant Store as SQLite KB Store
  participant Scanner as Scanner
  participant Repo as Local Repo
  participant AI as AI Package
  participant OpenAI as OpenAI API

  User->>CLI: contextos update retail-platform
  CLI->>Store: load registered repositories
  loop each repository
    CLI->>Scanner: scanRepository(repo)
    Scanner->>Repo: read Java, YAML, SQL, pom files
    Scanner-->>CLI: nodes + edges
    CLI->>Store: replaceGraphForRepository(repo, nodes, edges)
  end
  alt --generate-docs provided
    CLI->>Store: build repo/service/endpoint evidence
    CLI->>AI: generate docs from graph evidence
    alt OPENAI_API_KEY set
      AI->>OpenAI: synthesize explanatory Markdown
      OpenAI-->>AI: LLM docs
      AI-->>CLI: deterministic docs + LLM docs
    else no key or API failure
      AI-->>CLI: deterministic docs only
    end
    CLI->>Store: cache docs in SQLite
  else normal update
    CLI-->>User: graph refreshed, docs unchanged
  end
